description:
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;This advert is for attendees of the RCN Nursing Careers Fair (Midlands) on 4th Nov 2020.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;It was great to speak to some of you and tell you about coming to work for Leicestershire Partnership NHS Trust (LPT).&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We’re looking for Band 5 Staff Nurses (RGNs, RNMHs and RNLDs) to join us across the Trust in Leicestershire to help support on our Wards and Community Services.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We’re flexible on hours that you’d like to work and can offer permanent contracts and bank/casual roles to work around your current commitments.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Please see the benefits of working for LPT link. We may be able to offer relocation subject to meeting the criteria of our Trust policy.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If you’re unsure about whether you fit into the above criteria or if you are newly qualified, please still apply and we will be in touch with you.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If you are interested, please complete the application form and one of the team will be in touch to discuss further. If you’d like more information on the roles, please have a look at the attached Job Description.&lt;/p&gt;
